{
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.title": "失落之子们的信号",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.INITIAL.description": "久远之前散落的基因痕迹再次在群星间燃烧。马卡多指向星图上的四道残缺信号。每道信号尽头是哪位儿子，仍不得而知。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.INITIAL.options.SEARCH.title": "搜寻",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.INITIAL.options.SEARCH.description": "随机发现四位原体中的一位。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.INITIAL.options.LEAVE.title": "暂且停止",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.INITIAL.options.LEAVE.description": "无事发生。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.LEAVE.description": "舰队尚未准备就绪。你封存坐标，推迟搜寻。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.HORUS_FOUND.description": "[gold]发现：荷鲁斯·卢佩卡尔——克索尼亚[/gold] 第一位寻回的原体跪于帝皇面前。‘父亲，您终于找到我了。只需一声令下，我将使群星在您的名下俯首。’",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.HORUS_FOUND.options.CLAIM.title": "领取奖励",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.HORUS_FOUND.options.CLAIM.description": "获得[gold]乌兰诺凯旋[/gold]并得到[red]疑虑[/red]。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.SANGUINIUS_FOUND.description": "[gold]发现：圣吉列斯——巴尔·塞康达斯[/gold] 有翼原体收拢赤色羽翼，仰望帝皇。‘父亲，若我确是您的儿子，那么我相信这些羽翼是为守护人类而赐予我的。’",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.SANGUINIUS_FOUND.options.CLAIM.title": "领取奖励",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.SANGUINIUS_FOUND.options.CLAIM.description": "获得8点最大生命并回复8点生命。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.GUILLIMAN_FOUND.description": "[gold]发现：罗伯特·基里曼——马库拉格[/gold] 这位已建立文明的原体向帝皇庄重鞠躬。‘父亲，马库拉格的诸世界已准备就绪。我将为您的梦想带来秩序与律法。’",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.GUILLIMAN_FOUND.options.CLAIM.title": "领取奖励",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.GUILLIMAN_FOUND.options.CLAIM.description": "获得150金币，并选择1张牌升级。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.PERTURABO_FOUND.description": "[gold]发现：佩图拉博——奥林匹亚[/gold] 原体完成对石与钢的计算，等待帝皇的命令。‘父亲，请指出必须倒下的城墙。命令我在其上建立什么。’",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.PERTURABO_FOUND.options.CLAIM.title": "领取奖励",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.PERTURABO_FOUND.options.CLAIM.description": "选择2张牌升级并得到[red]疑虑[/red]。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.HORUS.description": "荷鲁斯是第一个回到你身边的儿子，成为征服的典范。但最明亮的星也投下最长的影。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.SANGUINIUS.description": "即使身处破碎的月亮，他仍在守护人类。他的高贵让即将到来的远征之伤显得轻了一些。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.GUILLIMAN.description": "他脚下的五百世界早已是一个帝国。比征服更罕见的，是保存既得之物的知识。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-PRIMARCH_SIGNALS.pages.PERTURABO.description": "没有堡垒能够承受他的计算。但每一场未被承认的胜利，都会在他心中筑起另一道墙。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-LORGARS_QUESTION.title": "这样的人怎会不是神？",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-LORGARS_QUESTION.pages.INITIAL.description": "‘若一人可夺取万千世界……若一人可孕育儿子守卫那些世界……若一人的思想可引领百万舰船穿越虚空……那么告诉我，父亲。这样的人怎会不是神？’",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-LORGARS_QUESTION.pages.INITIAL.options.DENY_DIVINITY.title": "+朕非神明。+",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-LORGARS_QUESTION.pages.INITIAL.options.DENY_DIVINITY.description": "获得一张升级的[gold]帝国真理[/gold]。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-LORGARS_QUESTION.pages.INITIAL.options.USE_THE_FAITH.title": "+信仰也可成为人类的工具。+",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-LORGARS_QUESTION.pages.INITIAL.options.USE_THE_FAITH.description": "获得200金币。升级随机1张普通牌与1张罕见牌。失去6点最大生命。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-LORGARS_QUESTION.pages.INITIAL.options.ENTRUST_MALCADOR.title": "+马卡多，处理此事。+",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-LORGARS_QUESTION.pages.INITIAL.options.ENTRUST_MALCADOR.description": "从牌组中移除1张牌。失去8点生命。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-LORGARS_QUESTION.pages.DENY_DIVINITY.description": "信仰被否定，真理被命令。但被命令的真理能否比信念活得更久？",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-LORGARS_QUESTION.pages.USE_THE_FAITH.description": "崇拜将军团与世界绑在一起。与此同时，人之皇帝与神之皇帝的界限开始崩坏。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-LORGARS_QUESTION.pages.ENTRUST_MALCADOR.description": "马卡多一言不发地封存记录。被推迟的争论并不会消失，只会在更深处滋长。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-KHORNE_TEMPTATION.title": "以鲜血终结",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-KHORNE_TEMPTATION.pages.INITIAL.description": "比战甲更庞大的黑暗从赤烟中升起。它不作争辩，只提供足以结束战争的力量，以及一个可供挥霍那力量的敌人。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-KHORNE_TEMPTATION.pages.INITIAL.options.REJECT.title": "+怒火只是朕意志的工具。+",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-KHORNE_TEMPTATION.pages.INITIAL.options.REJECT.description": "升级随机1张攻击牌。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-KHORNE_TEMPTATION.pages.INITIAL.options.ACCEPT.title": "+那么，让银河以鲜血作答。+",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-KHORNE_TEMPTATION.pages.INITIAL.options.ACCEPT.description": "失去8点最大生命。获得[gold]恐虐之印[/gold]。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-KHORNE_TEMPTATION.pages.REJECT.description": "赤色阴影退去。它的狂怒只留在应在之处：你的命令之下。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-KHORNE_TEMPTATION.pages.ACCEPT.description": "八次愤怒的搏动烙入你的灵魂。每场战斗都会在鲜血已然涌动时开始。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-TZEENTCH_TEMPTATION.title": "你难道早已知晓？",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-TZEENTCH_TEMPTATION.pages.INITIAL.description": "一个形体分裂成千张嘴与千对翅膀。每一张口都述说不同的未来，而每一个未来都是你几乎见过的。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-TZEENTCH_TEMPTATION.pages.INITIAL.options.REJECT.title": "+未来由人选择，而非侍奉。+",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-TZEENTCH_TEMPTATION.pages.INITIAL.options.REJECT.description": "升级随机1张技能牌。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-TZEENTCH_TEMPTATION.pages.INITIAL.options.ACCEPT.title": "+就连未见之路也将归于朕。+",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-TZEENTCH_TEMPTATION.pages.INITIAL.options.ACCEPT.description": "失去9点最大生命。获得[gold]奸奇之印[/gold]。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-TZEENTCH_TEMPTATION.pages.REJECT.description": "未来逐一闭合，直到只剩你脚下的道路。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-TZEENTCH_TEMPTATION.pages.ACCEPT.description": "九条道路同时展开。昔日的可能性成为每场战斗中第一道命令的形状。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-NURGLE_TEMPTATION.title": "放下痛苦",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-NURGLE_TEMPTATION.pages.INITIAL.description": "一张巨脸在荆棘与腐蝇间微笑。它并不许诺死亡，只许诺一种平静：伤口与绝望不再重要。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-NURGLE_TEMPTATION.pages.INITIAL.options.REJECT.title": "+疼痛证明朕仍然活着。+",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-NURGLE_TEMPTATION.pages.INITIAL.options.REJECT.description": "回复30%最大生命。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-NURGLE_TEMPTATION.pages.INITIAL.options.ACCEPT.title": "+若朕能忍受，腐朽亦非终局。+",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-NURGLE_TEMPTATION.pages.INITIAL.options.ACCEPT.description": "失去7点最大生命。获得[gold]纳垢之印[/gold]。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-NURGLE_TEMPTATION.pages.REJECT.description": "疼痛归来，尖锐而诚实。你将它视作使命仍属于自己的证据。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-NURGLE_TEMPTATION.pages.ACCEPT.description": "花园的七次呼吸沉入你的肺。它的耐心将随你进入每一场战斗。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-SLAANESH_TEMPTATION.title": "拥抱完美",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-SLAANESH_TEMPTATION.pages.INITIAL.description": "每断一条锁链，阴影便呈现更美的形态。它不说你可以变得完美；它低语你本已完美，只需放下最后的克制。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-SLAANESH_TEMPTATION.pages.INITIAL.options.REJECT.title": "+完美不是不受约束的欲望。+",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-SLAANESH_TEMPTATION.pages.INITIAL.options.REJECT.description": "从牌组中移除1张牌。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-SLAANESH_TEMPTATION.pages.INITIAL.options.ACCEPT.title": "+没有界限，便没有失败。+",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-SLAANESH_TEMPTATION.pages.INITIAL.options.ACCEPT.description": "失去6点最大生命。获得[gold]色孽之印[/gold]。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-SLAANESH_TEMPTATION.pages.REJECT.description": "无瑕的轮廓破碎。留下的不是完美，而是被拒绝磨砺出的纪律。",
  "MASTER_OF_MANKIND-SLAANESH_TEMPTATION.pages.ACCEPT.description": "六道束缚脱落。手的界限再也无法容纳你欲望的延伸。"
